      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  .kimlit-faq {\n    max-width: 850px;\n    margin: 35px auto;\n    padding: 0 15px;\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n  }\n\n  .kimlit-faq h2 {\n    text-align: center;\n    color: #0359ca;\n    font-size: 28px;\n    margin-bottom: 25px;\n  }\n\n  .kimlit-faq details {\n    background: #ffffff;\n    border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    padding: 16px 18px;\n    box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n  }\n\n  .kimlit-faq summary {\n    cursor: pointer;\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #222;\n    list-style: none;\n  }\n\n  .kimlit-faq summary::-webkit-details-marker {\n    display: none;\n  }\n\n  .kimlit-faq summary::after {\n    content: \"+\";\n    float: right;\n    color: #0359ca;\n    font-size: 22px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n  }\n\n  .kimlit-faq details[open] summary::after {\n    content: \"-\";\n  }\n\n  .kimlit-faq p {\n    margin-top: 12px;\n    color: #555;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"kimlit-faq\">\n  <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n\n  <details>\n    <summary>Is the keyboard wireless?</summary>\n    <p>Yes, this portable foldable keyboard connects wirelessly, making it easy to use with your phone, tablet, or laptop without extra cables.</p>\n  </details>\n\n  <details>\n    <summary>Does it have a touchpad?</summary>\n    <p>Yes, it includes a built-in touchpad so you can control your device easily without needing a separate mouse.</p>\n  </details>\n\n  <details>\n    <summary>Is it easy to carry?</summary>\n    <p>Yes, the foldable design makes it compact and lightweight, perfect for travel, work, school, or daily use.</p>\n  </details>\n\n  <details>\n    <summary>Is it rechargeable?</summary>\n    <p>Yes, the keyboard is rechargeable, so you can use it conveniently without replacing batteries.</p>\n  </details>\n\n  <details>\n    <summary>What devices can I use it with?</summary>\n    <p>It is suitable for many devices such as smartphones, tablets, laptops, and other compatible devices that support wireless keyboard connection.</p>\n  </details>\n\n  <details>\n    <summary>How long does delivery take?</summary>\n    <p>Delivery usually takes around 5–7 business days. You can contact us anytime through WhatsApp for order updates or support.</p>\n  </details>\n</div>",
